const faqs = [
  { q: 'Is the Sennheiser Momentum 4 better than the Sony WH-1000XM5?', a: 'It depends on your priorities. The Momentum 4 has better sound quality (warmer, more detailed midrange), triple the battery life (60 hours vs 20 hours), and more comfortable earpads for long sessions. The Sony XM5 has stronger active noise cancellation, a more modern design, better touch controls, and superior call quality. If you care about sound and battery above all, get the Momentum 4. If you want the best ANC and a sleeker look, get the Sony.' },
